# Local Development

- Node and tooling: see [`package.json`](mdc:package.json) for scripts.
- Next.js app root: [`src/app`](mdc:src/app). Entry layout at [`src/app/layout.tsx`](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx).
- Run dev server: `npm run dev`.
- Lint before commit: `npm run lint`.
- When editing, avoid large, unrelated refactors; keep edits scoped.
- Prefer absolute paths in workspace when scripting.